### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

###

### Database Test
GET http://localhost:3000/api/test

###

### Get All Locations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/locations

###

### SCENARIO 1: Location 1 - PASS (sufficient recent data)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/locations/1/data-sufficiency

###

### View Reports for Location 1
GET http://localhost:3000/api/locations/1/reports

###

### SCENARIO 2: Location 2 - FAIL (insufficient data)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/locations/2/data-sufficiency

###

### SCENARIO 3: Location 3 - FAIL (stale data)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/locations/3/data-sufficiency

###